Privacy Policy
We take the privacy of children very seriously,                                                                                          especially as teachers and parents ourselves.
Please find full details below on what our apps do and do not include.
Learning Station apps:
Do NOT collect, access or transmit any personal information.
Do NOT contain any third party advertising.
DO include a locked parent area which includes links for emailing our support team and links to our website, Facebook page and to the app store.
DO ask for access to the microphone in order to allow you to record the books. You can turn this option off in Settings.
PAID apps do NOT contain any in-app purchases.
FREE apps DO contain in-app purchases which are protected by the parental gate.
Please contact us at
support@readingtrain.org
with any questions.
Last update to Privacy Policy: March 3, 2020